# NeoLex Advanced Dictionary

![NeoLex Logo](images/neolex-logo.png)

NeoLex is a state-of-the-art, feature-rich dictionary web application designed to provide an immersive and comprehensive language exploration experience. With its sleek interface and advanced functionality, NeoLex goes beyond simple word lookups to offer a deep dive into language and etymology.

## Table of Contents

- [Features](#features)
- [Demo](#demo)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [API Keys](#api-keys)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
- [License](#license)
- [Contact](#contact)

## Features

- **Comprehensive Word Information**: Detailed results including definitions, part of speech, phonetics, etymology, synonyms, and antonyms.
- **Text-to-Speech**: Hear the correct pronunciation of words with a single click.
- **Favorites**: Save and quickly access your favorite words.
- **Search History**: Keep track of your recent searches for easy reference.
- **Word Suggestions**: Get real-time word suggestions as you type.
- **Word of the Day**: Expand your vocabulary with a daily featured word.
- **Customizable Themes**: Choose from Dark, Light, and Neon themes to suit your preference.
- **Adjustable Font Size**: Customize the app's text size for better readability.
- **Responsive Design**: Enjoy a seamless experience across desktop and mobile devices.
- **Keyboard Navigation**: Easily navigate the app using keyboard shortcuts.
- **Easter Egg**: Discover a hidden surprise with the Konami Code!

## Demo

